# SuperMarketAppManagement
This program is used to manage the shops item.
In this program just used simple logic behind the supermarket application how the application 
performs and what are the necessary task need to perform, in this program the following task can be perform,
=========Welcome to the supermarket========
1. View items
2. Add items for sale
3. Purchase items
4. Search items
5. Edit items
6. Exit
accordingly. for example the output is shown below,

